<P>
   SKUBE-BEER _ The first thing to get straight is the apostrophe.
It's Tuppers' Hop Pocket Ale, not Tupper's. God is in the details,
one of the philosophers said, and there's something of the divine
in this beer just now arriving in the Atlanta market. (Skube,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED .
</P>
<P>
   FOOD-ITALIAN _ Be your own guest. Now, that's a dinner party
concept you ought to be able to sink your teeth into. It's taken
from the Tuscans. (Longino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
