<P>
   FOOD-RECIPIES _ It's your small dinner party. You're the host.
And food experts such as Molly O'Neill say you ``must appear cool
and unruffled, offhand in attitude, disposed to easy and amiable
chat.'' (Longino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   RECIPE-SWAP _ The reason we love Snickers bars is the gooey
combination of chocolate, nuts and soft caramel. That's the same
reason you'll love a Snickers Cake, a decadent descendant of the
beloved candy bar. (Walker, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
