<P>
   TRAVEL-NANTAHALA _ BRYSON CITY, N.C. -- The Nantahala Outdoor
Center offers a wide array of activities for those who like to suck
in their outdoors in big gulps. Located on both banks of the
Nantahala River in the narrow and steep Nantahala Gorge, the NOC is
best known as a whitewater haven. (Brice, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) MOVED FOR SUNDAY.
