beginning Saturday, July 18.
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is the CoxNet weekend budget for the weekend beginning
Saturday, July 18. This budget will be updated every afternoon
through the week. Questions about stories from Cox newspapers on
this budget should be directed to CoxNet, the Cox News Service, in
Atlanta at 800-950-3739 or 404-526-5456.
