   GLENN _ WASHINGTON _ America may be waiting for Sen. John
Glenn's return to glory in October, but Glenn himself is not. For
Glenn, who turned 77 on Saturday (July 18) the glory is already
back. (Montgomery, Cox News Service).
</P>
