<HEADLINE>
IT'S OFFICIAL: `60 MINUTES' GETS DOUBLE
</HEADLINE>
   (also moving in `f' category) 
(rm) 
 By BILL CARTER   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   PASADENA, Calif. _ CBS made it official Wednesday: ``60
Minutes,'' the oldest and most successful news program in the
history of television, will expand to a second edition early next
