</P>
<P>
   In addition, the correspondents had expressed their own
reservations about the potential risk to the reputation of the
original. But CBS's management pushed the expansion to take
advantage of the ``60 Minutes'' name. News magazines are some of
the most dependable profit centers for networks, which are under
