<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-15 22:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7265 &Cx1f; taf-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-EDIT-RENO-NYT &LR;      07-15 0522
